SYNOPSIS
  wizmode
  wizmode [on | off]  

DESCRIPTION
  For easier debugging/experiencing of the games as wizard, it is
  possible to switch off some of the wizardry powers.

  If the wizmode is off, wizards
   - aren't able to see in the dark.
   - can't see hidden exits.
   - may die.

  The wizmode command is connected with the property P_NOWIZ, is this
  is non-zero, the wizmode is off.

EXAMPLES
  wizmode      : shows the current wizmode setting.
  wizmode on   : switches the wizmode back on
  wizmode off  : switches the wizmode off
